address.streetAddress: Sandhill Traditional Plan, Munhall Glen of St. Charles

location.fullValue: Sandhill Traditional Plan, Munhall Glen of St. Charles

data.description: Ranch home with 3 beds & 3 Baths already under construction, but there's still some time to pick your finishes! This home will include a full, finished basement, LP siding, Oakwood flooring, an over-sized 2.5 car garage, and so many more amazing finishes! Located on a quiet cul-de-sac in a desirable neighborhood close to nature paths, schools, and shopping. The City of St. Charles is known as the "Pride of the Fox" for its presence along the famous Fox River. Downtown St. Charles has been recognized as a "Top 10" for fine dining, arts, entertainment, and recreational opportunities. Located in award-winning St. Charles School District 303. This location is prime!
